              | and were mindful of my price range."
            footer.quote-footer
              cite.quote-author Chloe M.
                a.quote-author-link(href="/city/philadelphia") Philadelphia
          img(src="/images/testimonials/chloe.png", alt="Chloe M, Philadelphia")

